<p>The settlement in the copyright <a href="https://dailynous.com/2025/08/28/class-action-lawsuit-against-ai-firm-for-copyright-infringement/">lawsuit against Anthropic</a> provides authors of books they trained their AI on with compensation.<span id="more-55225"></span></p>
<p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="wp-image-55226 aligncenter" src="https://dailynous.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/anthropic-book-piracy-settlement-1024x839.png" alt="" width="489" height="400" srcset="https://dailynous.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/anthropic-book-piracy-settlement-1024x839.png 1024w, https://dailynous.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/anthropic-book-piracy-settlement-300x246.png 300w, https://dailynous.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/anthropic-book-piracy-settlement-768x629.png 768w, https://dailynous.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/anthropic-book-piracy-settlement-400x328.png 400w, https://dailynous.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/anthropic-book-piracy-settlement.png 1405w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 489px) 100vw, 489px" /></p>
<p>The amount of compensation ultimately depends on the number of people who file a claim, but estimates are that claimants will receive a little under $3000 per book.</p>
<p>The total settlement fund is $1.5 billion.</p>
<p>You can check whether you are eligible to submit a claim by searching <a href="https://secure.anthropiccopyrightsettlement.com/lookup/?_gl=1r42ccv_gcl_auMTk3OTU2MjA3MC4xNzU5NzU1NDM2" target="_blank" rel="noopener">this database of books</a>.Â You can submit a claim <a href="https://secure.anthropiccopyrightsettlement.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">here</a>.</p>
<p>Claims must be submitted by March 23rd, 2026.</p><p>The post <a href="https://dailynous.com/2025/10/06/if-anthropic-used-your-work-you-could-be-entitled-to-compensation/">If Anthropic Used Your Work, You Could be Entitled to Compensation</a> first appeared on <a href="https://dailynous.com">Daily Nous</a>.</p>